verbose_text: The specific results of our study indicate that the expression of miR-451 was up-regulated relative to the control group after the transfecting miR-451 mimics, and was down-regulated to some extent after transfecting miR-451 inhibitors in MCF-7, MCF-7 / EPI, and MCF-7 / DOC cells, but no without statistical significance, which may lead to the inherent low level of miR-451 expression in breast cancer cells.
